{"tid":805042,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌","createTime":"2018-09-03T13:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T20:22:00.000Z","uid":11506,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1364c7fc7a2ea67097d9b25ac727b8c9f02ab8fe","tid":805042,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20edf24be82c247e997b4ca320a228e5c59596f8","tid":805042,"uid":87762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"條友而家去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de333f801ab53dbd941ccb575f516ba3d72d1af8","tid":805042,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"開學竟然冇人貼哩篇 有啲意外"},{"pid":"115128bb776a2cb5807e5f1af1e4790aec36843f","tid":805042,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20edf24be82c247e997b4ca320a228e5c59596f8","tid":805042,"uid":87762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"條友而家去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"ou bba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好快有第一桶金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7181a7ca80fb15fda488d7c0c78e2c532bc8f0d","tid":805042,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,